Bora of <a href="http://scienceblogs.com/clock/">A Blog Around The Clock</a> has edited an anthology of the best fifty posts from science and medical blogs in 2006: <a href="http://scienceblogs.com/clock/2007/01/the_science_blogging_anthology.php"><i>The Open Laboratory: The Best Writing on Science Blogs 2006</i></a>.  The Panda's Thumb is represented by Ian Musgrave's post, <a href="http://www.pandasthumb.org/archives/2006/11/denton_vs_squid.html">Denton vs Squid; the eye as suboptimal design</a>.  Several other Pandites represent their personal blogs in the anthology as well.

You can order yourself a copy of the anthology from <a href="http://www.lulu.com/content/631016">Lulu</a>.

Congrats to all the winners.

